stories.text: Last night when I couldn't sleep one of the things that went through my head is the difference between the pejorative and non-pejorative meaning for hacker, for the non-pejorative I wanted to come up with an example for a hack would illustrate the concept but the things that started to come to mind were in programming. Rather than devote more time to it in my head I figured I could go through a bunch of lifehacks links but maybe it would be better to ask HN what you consider to be the top clever hacks that you would use to explain the non-pejorative meaning.
